Name: Diefrosty
About the game: Diefrosty is an unsurvival puzzle game, where your one and only goal is to kill your ice-cuby character no matter how. Intereract with many obstacles, use really dumb ways to die while melting your brain to beat each level. Interact with diverse obstacles and ways to kill your character! To get to the next level you might have to die in dumb ways while also going through really hard puzzle levels in this friendly cartoon puzzle kill the character simulator.
